// How to run

Install deps:
npm install
Initialize Prisma client and DB:
npx prisma generate
npx prisma migrate dev --name init
Start the service:
npm run dev
Optional: open data browser
npx prisma studio

//Endpoints

POST /products 201: create product
Body: { name, description, price, tags }
GET /products/:id 200/404: detail (id, name, description, price, tags, createdAt)
PATCH /products/:id 200/404: partial update
DELETE /products/:id 204/404
GET /products 200: list with offset pagination, sort, search
Query: offset, limit, sort=recent, q

//Notes

tags is stored as JSON array due to SQLite; validated as string[].
price is Decimal in DB; serialized to number in API.
Added optional helpful fields: slug (unique), status, stock without changing required API contracts.
